In both cases, the `Length` implementation will vary depending on whether you're looking at a single segment or a series of connected segments (the implementation wasn't provided as it's straightforward for line segments and an iterative sum for polylines). 

These are just general points to consider. You'll need to determine how much complexity is necessary based on the needs of your game engine. Always strive for simplicity and clarity in your class designs.

